creator: Buildup Studio
descriptionHtml:
■ You're gonna camp with cats!
What interesting things are gonna happen at the cat campsite?

■ Have a time to relax at campsite!
Enjoy atmosphere of campsite that changes every morning, evening and season.
Feel the nature at the forest camp where you can hear the sound of waves and grass bugs and lighthouse beach.

■ Decorate campsite with various camping gear?
From Nordic tent to ethnic style, you can decorate everything you want!
Collect various camping props and accessories to spruce up cats!

■ Try to cook camping dishes!
from Ramyeon to hotpot to paella, Learn more than 150 kinds of camping recipes!
You can get fresh ingredients from garden and barrel fishing!

■ If you decorate the campsite and cook, your campsite will be crowded with animal friends soon
Have a chat with animal friends who visit your campsite!
Invite buskers to have a camping party.

■ How did other friends decorate the campsite?
Invite your friends and go to their campsite.
Meet special animal friends that you can only meet there.

■ Camping with Cats!
Now start!

Animal camping is an emotional camping simulation game that you can camp with cats in nature.

* If you can't log in to Google, please restart the game after cleansing the data/cache of the Google Play game and Google Play service app.

Data/Cache Delete Path: Settings → Application →
Select Google Play Games / Google Play Services → Storage → Click 'Delete Data', 'Delete Cache'

* Visit animal camping community!
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/animal_camping/

* Please send inquiry related to technical issues or purchase by email!
Mail: buildupstudiocontact@gmail.com

* Essential access permissions
The game requires your permission to:
- WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
- READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
These rights are are not used for any other purpose than video ad, saving the date and screenshots. This game would not use the permissions for any other use than mentioned.

title: Animal Camping

creator: Buildup Studio
descriptionHtml:
■ You have gone camping with the cats.
What fun things will happen at the cat campsite?

■ Busy, busy campsite management!
Solve the quests of various animal friends and raise the level of the campsite.
Create your own campsite management strategy.

■ Decorate the campsite to your liking!
From a tent with a Scandinavian sense to a comical style, decorate the campsite with various camping equipment.
Collect more than 300 kinds of camping supplies and cute cat crew costumes.

■ Challenge delicious camping cuisine!
From noodles to world-class dishes, learn more than 150 kinds of camping recipes.
Find ingredients in the vegetable garden, the mudflat, and the fishtrap and cook them right away.

■ Visit your friend's campsite!
Explore the mudflat at your friend's campsite and find treasures.
Give gifts to friends and boast about your campsite.

■ Your own secret hideaway!
Enjoy the changing seasons and days and nights of the campsite in real time.
Invite buskers to have a camping party and recover yourself while listening to the sound of waves and grasshoppers.

■ New event updates every month!
Don't miss out, start now!

Animal camping is a camping simulation game where you can enjoy camping in nature with cats.

title: Animal Camping

■ You have gone camping with the cats.
What fun things will happen at the cat campsite?

■ Your own secret hideaway!
Enjoy the changing seasons and days and nights of the campsite in real time.
Invite buskers to have a camping party and recover yourself while listening to the sound of waves and grasshoppers.

■ Decorate the campsite to your liking!
From a tent with a Scandinavian sense to a comical style, decorate the campsite with various camping equipment.
Collect more than 300 kinds of camping supplies and cute cat crew costumes.

■ Challenge delicious camping cuisine!
From noodles to world-class dishes, learn more than 150 kinds of camping recipes.
Find ingredients in the vegetable garden, the mudflat, and the fishtrap and cook them right away.

■ Busy, busy campsite management!

Create your own campsite management strategy.

■ Visit your friend's campsite!
Explore the mudflat at your friend's campsite and find treasures.
Give gifts to friends and boast about your campsite.

■ New event updates every month!
Don't miss out, start now!

descriptionHtml:
■ You, who have come to the campsite to escape from the busy daily life.
What if one day, you suddenly go camping with the cats?

■ Your own secret hideaway!
Enjoy the changing seasons and days and nights of the campsite in real time.
Invite buskers to have a camping party and recover yourself while listening to the sound of waves and grasshoppers.

■ Decorate the campsite to your liking!
From a tent with a Scandinavian sense to a comical style, decorate the campsite with various camping equipment.
Collect more than 300 kinds of camping supplies and cute cat crew costumes.

■ Challenge delicious camping cuisine!
From noodles to world-class dishes, learn more than 150 kinds of camping recipes.
Find ingredients in the vegetable garden, the mudflat, and the fishtrap and cook them right away.

■ Busy, busy campsite management!
Solve the quests of various animal friends and raise the level of the campsite.
Create your own campsite management strategy.

■ Visit your friend's campsite!
Explore the mudflat at your friend's campsite and find treasures.
Give gifts to friends and boast about your campsite.

Animal camping is a camping simulation game where you can enjoy camping in nature with cats.

* If you can't log in to Google, please restart the game after cleansing the data/cache of the Google Play game and Google Play service app.

Data/Cache Delete Path: Settings → Application →
Select Google Play Games / Google Play Services → Storage → Click 'Delete Data', 'Delete Cache'

* Visit animal camping community!
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/animal_camping/

* Please send inquiry related to technical issues or purchase by email!
Mail: buildupstudiocontact@gmail.com

* Essential access permissions
The game requires your permission to:
- WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
- READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
These rights are are not used for any other purpose than video ad, saving the date and screenshots. This game would not use the permissions for any other use than mentioned.
descriptionShort: Chill and relaxing camping with cats
